elements.name: Validate Television Review Page with filters

steps.name: I am on the Home Page "https://www.which.co.uk/reviews/televisions" of Which Website
the Screen size is selected as "20-28"
the Screen type is "LCD"
I see the Television review display for the filters that is applied

elements.name: Validate Television Review Page with Sort By

steps.name: I am on the Home Page "https://www.which.co.uk/reviews/televisions" of Which Website
the sort by is selected as "Price (low to high)"
I see the Television review display according to the sort by option
I am able to scroll up and down
I select "3" television product with "Add to Compare" to compare the product
I see that the selected products are added to compare pool
the option " Add to compare " is changed to "Remove from compare"
I select compare
the user is navigated to "Compare Television - Which?" screen
the added products to be compared are seen

elements.name: Validate Television Review Page with different menu - say Best Buy

steps.name: I am on the Home Page "https://www.which.co.uk/reviews/televisions" of Which Website
the user select "Best Buy"
the user is navigated to "  Best Buy televisions - Which?"
the page is refershed
I see the webpage is still "  Best Buy televisions - Which?"
